'''Aniruddha Bose''' (born 11 April 1959) is an Indian judge and Chief Justice of [[Jharkhand High Court]]
==Career== Bose passed Higher Secondary Examination from [[St. Lawrence High School, Kolkata]] in 1976 and passed B.Com. from [[St. Xavier's College, Kolkata|St. Xavier's College]] in [[Kolkata]]. He completed the [[LL.B]]. from [[Surendranath Law College]]. After the enrollment he started practise on Constitutional, Civil and Intellectual Property matters in the [[Calcutta High Court]] in 1985. Bose worked in the Original Side as well as the Appellate Side of the High Court. He was elevated as permanent Judge of the Calcutta High Court in January 2004.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.calcuttahighcourt.gov.in/Judges/26|title=The Hon'ble Justice Aniruddha Bose|last=|first=|date=|website=calcuttahighcourt.gov.in|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=October 19, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dailypioneer.com/2018/state-editions/justice-aniruddha-bose-takes-oath-as-12th-chief-justice-of-jhc.html|title=Justice Aniruddha Bose takes oath as 12th Chief Justice of JHC|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=October 19, 2018}}</ref> His name was recommended for elevation as the Chief Justice of [[Delhi High Court]] but returned by the [[Government of India]], with the observation that he does not have the experience to handle the affairs of a prominent High Court like Delhi. The collegium reconsidered the proposal and he was transferred to Jharkhanad High Court as Chief Justice on 4 August 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livelaw.in/justice-aniruddha-bose-appointed-as-chief-justice-of-jharkhand-high-court-read-notification/|title=Justice Aniruddha Bose Appointed As Chief Justice Of Jharkhand High Court|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=October 19, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://barandbench.com/justice-aniruddha-bose-misses-ticket-delhi-now-jharkhand-high-court-chief-justice/|title=Justice Aniruddha Bose misses ticket to Delhi, now recommended as Jharkhand High Court CJ|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=October 19, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/sc-collegium-recommends-justice-aniruddha-boses-name-for-appointment-as-jharkhand-hc-cj-5268212/|title=SC Collegium recommends Justice Aniruddha Bose’s name for appointment as Jharkhand HC CJ|last=|first=|date=|website=indianexpress.com|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=October 19, 2018}}</ref>
